@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_suoftn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v2 + 0.06)) / v2)
    tmp = wp.exp(0.90)
    tmp = v2
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.40) - (tmp + 0.01 + v2 + 0.61)) + 0.23)
    v1 = 0.41
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.72)) - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.02) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.52)))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = 0.35
    data[tid] = v0
